{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MediaSource.addSourceBuffer()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/addSourceBuffer","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Media_Source_Extensions_API\">Media Source Extensions API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource\"><code>MediaSource</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/MediaSource\"><code>MediaSource()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/activeSourceBuffers\"><code>activeSourceBuffers</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/duration\"><code>duration</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/sourceBuffers\"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><em><code>addSourceBuffer()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/clearLiveSeekableRange\"><code>clearLiveSeekableRange()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/endOfStream\"><code>endOfStream()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/isTypeSupported\"><code>isTypeSupported()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/removeSourceBuffer\"><code>removeSourceBuffer()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/setLiveSeekableRange\"><code>setLiveSeekableRange()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Media Source Extensions に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement/getVideoPlaybackQuality\"><code>HTMLVideoElement.getVideoPlaybackQuality()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer\"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBufferList\"><code>SourceBufferList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>TextTrack.sourceBuffer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VideoPlaybackQuality\"><code>VideoPlaybackQuality</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VideoTrack/sourceBuffer\"><code>VideoTrack.sourceBuffer</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource\"><code>MediaSource</code></a> インターフェイスの <strong><code>addSourceBuffer()</code></strong> メソッドは、指定された <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/MIME_type\">MIME タイプ</a>の新しい <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer\"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> を作成し、<code>MediaSource</code> の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/sourceBuffers\" title=\"sourceBuffers\"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a> リストに追加します。 新しい <code>SourceBuffer</code> も返されます。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>sourceBuffer</em> = <em>mediaSource</em>.addSourceBuffer(<em>mimeType</em>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"パラメーター","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"mimetype\"><code>mimeType</code></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource\"><code>MediaSource</code></a> に作成して追加する <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer\"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> の MIME タイプを指定する <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>作成され、メディアソースに追加された新しいソースバッファを表す <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer\"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> オブジェクト。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"例外","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"invalidaccesserror\"><code>InvalidAccessError</code></dt>\n <dd><code>mimeType</code> に指定された値は、有効な MIME タイプではなく空の文字列です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"invalidstateerror\"><code>InvalidStateError</code></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource\"><code>MediaSource</code></a> の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/readyState\" title=\"readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a> は <code>\"open\"</code> でありません。</dd>\n <dt id=\"notsupportederror\"><code>NotSupportedError</code></dt>\n <dd>指定された <code>mimeType</code> は<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/User_agent\">ユーザーエージェント</a>でサポートされていないか、メディアソースの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/sourceBuffers\" title=\"sourceBuffers\"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a> リストに既に含まれている他の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer\"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a> オブジェクトの MIME タイプと互換性がありません。</dd>\n <dt id=\"quotaexceedederror\"><code>QuotaExceededError</code></dt>\n <dd>ユーザーエージェントはこれ以上 <code>SourceBuffer</code> オブジェクトを処理できないか、指定された <code>mimeType</code> を使用して新しい <code>SourceBuffer</code> を作成すると、<a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#sourcebuffer-configuration\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SourceBuffer の構成がサポートされなくなります</a>。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>次のスニペットは、Nick Desaulniers によって書かれた簡単な例からのものです（<a href=\"http://nickdesaulniers.github.io/netfix/demo/bufferAll.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ライブで完全なデモを見る</a>か、<a href=\"https://github.com/nickdesaulniers/netfix/blob/gh-pages/demo/bufferAll.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ソースをダウンロード</a>してさらに調査してください）。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js  language-js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> assetURL <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'frag_bunny.mp4'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Blink はコーデックに関して特定する必要がある</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ./mp4info frag_bunny.mp4 | grep Codec</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> mimeCodec <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'video/mp4; codecs=\"avc1.42E01E, mp4a.40.2\"'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'MediaSource'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> window <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> MediaSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isTypeSupported</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mimeCodec<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> mediaSource <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MediaSource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//console.log(mediaSource.readyState); // closed</span>\n  video<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>src <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createObjectURL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mediaSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  mediaSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'sourceopen'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sourceOpen<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'サポートされていない MIME タイプまたはコーデック: '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> mimeCodec<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">sourceOpen</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">_</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//console.log(this.readyState); // open</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> mediaSource <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> sourceBuffer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> mediaSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addSourceBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mimeCodec<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetchAB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>assetURL<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">buf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    sourceBuffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'updateend'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">_</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      mediaSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">endOfStream</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      video<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">play</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">//console.log(mediaSource.readyState); // ended</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    sourceBuffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buf<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/media-source/#idl-def-mediasource-addsourcebuffer(domstring)\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Media Source Extensions<br><small lang=\"ja\">addSourceBuffer() の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaSource.addSourceBuffer","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/addSourceBuffer/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer\"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBufferList\"><code>SourceBufferList</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"MediaSource インターフェイスの addSourceBuffer() メソッドは、指定された MIME タイプの新しい SourceBuffer を作成し、MediaSource の sourceBuffers リストに追加します。 新しい SourceBuffer も返されます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MediaSource.addSourceBuffer()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MediaSource.addSourceBuffer()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/mediasource/addsourcebuffer","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/mediasource/addsourcebuffer/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource","title":"MediaSource"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/addSourceBuffer","title":"MediaSource.addSourceBuffer()"}],"pageTitle":"MediaSource.addSourceBuffer() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}